parameters: I'm in a little something over here!
Do it in the toilet, dammit.
Everyone tells me to do it in the toilet and all,
but it feels really good to do it here.
THIS IS THE ENERGY GENERATION FACILITY.
IT'S BETTER IF YOU STAY AWAY.
There's a residential area east from here.
I wanna see how it looks like for myself,
but us outworld residents aren't allowed in...
You can buy daily necessities on the first floor
and clothes on the second floor.
By the way, someone explains this exact thing inside.
They also sell clothes for girls like me.
